### Downgrade Node 9 in MacOS
$ brew install node@8 // just install node8 side by side
$ brew unlink node    // unlink old one
$ brew link node@8    // link node version 8

### Virtualenv 
pip install nodeenv
nodeenv -p --node=4.2.2
# The nodeenv -p option will install node into your python venv which will make your life easier probably.